the government evacuation program for byelorussia is based on 
people who are at risk of being exposed to 35 rems during a 
lifetime a rem is the standard unit of measurement for the amount 
of radiation absorbed by living tissue 
thirtyfive rems is 35000 millirems the typical diagnostic 
chest xray involves between 20 millirems and 30 millirems of 
radiation 
