25foot steel cable which stretched from a 280pound sofa in his 
living room to form a collar around his neck by dining with 
friends and later jogged two miles 
a former marathon runner warren developed severe respiratory 
problems from smoking cigarettes 
warren an artist dog trainer and drug counselor said he 
unsuccessfully tried everything to end his nicotine addiction he 
finally resorted to having his friends chain him up on july 9 and 
rid his home of tobacco 
warren said some people laughed at his plan 
i had some people who said sarcastically couldnt you do it 
on your own there are some people who cant do it on their own 
they need to be tied up or in treatment he said 
