charred 8630 acres in the glacier complex on the malheur national 
forest 22 miles east of john day in eastcentral oregon said 
spokeswoman barbara kennedy 
in southern california a 5845acre fire in the cleveland 
national forest east of san diego remained out of control monday 
but a 1200acre brush fire northwest of los angeles which earlier 
forced 100 people to evacuate was controlled 
about 1270 firefighters had the cleveland blaze about 55 
